{"tid":1966152,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"單睪丸貓仔絕育！！","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T01:04:58.000Z","uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6964e91fe68a54f234f501f38ebf7929c3234eb5","tid":1966152,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:50:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的 屋企隻貓仔就快一歲<br />\n呢排開日日始叫春想幫佢搵絕育<br />\n但係前排有啲病帶去睇醫生先知道佢係天生單睪丸<br />\n（即係得一隻睪丸外露 另一隻係個肚到）<br />\n醫生話如果唔盡快絕育之後發情期會嘔<br />\n第一次貓仔黎 冇太多醫生經驗 想問下各位巴絲會唔會有邊度做呢類既絕育手術安全推薦🙏🏼唔該！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw我係荃灣區 之前隻貓眼潰瘍睇荃灣點知越睇越衰轉介咗第二間⋯⋯診所係邊度都冇所謂最緊要安全可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407ae907d00f341bbaec898fe222f52f4ff6fe30","tid":1966152,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bcffc758ebb75fb06030054d98338503a033122","tid":1966152,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"灣仔皇后大道東獸醫診所<br />\n好好既獸醫，又唔會呃人亂驗野<br />\n但有冇做過單春絕育手術就唔知<br />\n我d貓都係佢到絕育"},{"pid":"868a62d8f0b2cca736d79c9e1ae5acd9bd0e5c28","tid":1966152,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bcffc758ebb75fb06030054d98338503a033122","tid":1966152,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"灣仔皇后大道東獸醫診所<br />\n好好既獸醫，又唔會呃人亂驗野<br />\n但有冇做過單春絕育手術就唔知<br />\n我d貓都係佢到絕育"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:26:05.000Z","msg":"好呀唔該絲打！<br />\n你個陣total圍返大概幾錢呀"},{"pid":"fb91a80d4a1403fecad0b0b305786f3c02fc3fca","tid":1966152,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"868a62d8f0b2cca736d79c9e1ae5acd9bd0e5c28","tid":1966152,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bcffc758ebb75fb06030054d98338503a033122","tid":1966152,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep